         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Success! The Bhagavant, Bodhisattva Ayita (Skt. Ajita), the future Buddha, commissioned by the <foreign>upāsaka</foreign> Visāgha (Skt. Viśākha) of the Vāgāḍhica family, together with his son<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied>, for the well-being and happiness of the whole world.</p>
         </div>
